included.description: Working as a User Experience Fellow on the design of a University of Michigan Web System that caters to on demand tracking of students performances by advisors. It is a early warning system for academic advisors. It is basically to make life easier for the advisors to track their student performances and gather relations between items that affect a student performance and also help them guide students based upon that information.
included.title: User Experience Fellow

included.description: A state of the art, portfolio & event management system for Arts Circles. Identified from a personally experienced problem, it carries the emotions of the users perfectly. A social mashup of Facebook, Twitter, Google+, YouTube, Flickr & Timeline.js, the product aims at decreasing the time lag that exists due to information asymmetry in manual events management. For the management, Artystic is "Find the right people with the right skills"â. For the users Artystic is about "Let the people know about you. Be the architect of your future."
included.title: Arts Circle event management system.

included.description: One of the main services that the organization provides is Vocational Skills Training and Employment Services to the intellectually disabled. There is currently a process in place to document the activities & work that the disabled learners do during their training at the organization, but no way to determine their progress and success as each person is very unique. The design challenge for contextual enquiry proposed is to thoroughly research their training processes from both organizational as well as people perspectives to find any problems that might exist in the current processes. The next step is to use that data to find a way to determine the progress of the people and also define a success metric for the organization.
included.title: Contextual inquiry of business processes in a huge organization

included.description: It started with a staunch determination to create a product that could increase the efficiency of the assembly line by timely scheduling of preventive maintenance jobs of the newspaper printing machines. With a innovative multi-level time based scheduler & a single click UI for shop floor workers Prevent.ive maximized the customers productivity. With cost management,admin dashboard, archival job tracking, maintenance report generation, the product catered to covering all use cases for a optimized maintenance tool.
included.title: Job Scheduler for Preventive Maintenance of Newapaper Printing Machines

included.description: The focus of Medilyzer was to provide a system that can help analyze trends in medical ailments that persist in a particular age in students. Falling into the domain of predictive analysis, the crux of the product was around a visualization framework that can help doctors at various geographical locations analyze the data together. With sophisticated multi level graphing, the medical data could be analyzed in terms of organs,age,ailments,heridatory diseases,class of students etc. With detailed medical reports and porting, the product received a great response from the doctors and is live today.
included.title: Web based medical profile management and analytics system.

included.description:
The product VIZI is aimed at making the process of using a band-aid easier for those using it with one hand. The concept is basically of combining bandaids + stickers into a poster. This product is designed to look and act like a regular band-aid by protecting wounds from infection and supporting the bodyâs healing process. Additionally it is meant to change the way people interact with band-aids, by making them more accessible to all, especially to those with the use of only one hand.

The poster aspect of the product is also intended to make the band-aids easier to find. One no longer has to remember where the band-aid box is stored since there is now easy access to them on the wall or another flat surface. The product aims to make the process of healing wounds and applying bandaids joyful with its fun and interactive designs.
included.title: Vizi - Product Design

included.description: Green Travel is a Vehicle mounted, Sustainable USB charging and Travel analysis system which we built using collaborative speed profiling. Green Travel consists of two parts. The first being a sustainable vehicle mounted mobile charger that works upon the wind energy generated as the vehicle crosses a speed of 25km/hr. The second being an analytics system mining traffic as well as user driving related information from the speed variations in driving.
included.title: Vehicle Mounted Mobile Charging and Travel Analytics system

ingredients at home and wanted a faster way to figure out what they can cook out of it and do it
in as less time as possible. This is where the foundation of Ingradient âlies.
included.title: Ingradient - Interaction Design

included.description: Aimed at providing a complete on the fly root cause analysis dashboarding framework, Monitor. ME structures itself dynamically on the basis of user interactions and inputs. With very innovative multiple data source metric aggregation and visualization, the UI is the show stopper. Customized time resolutions, zooming options, dashboard save and load, on hover graph modification. The product has just what is needed to find a root cause of a software infrastructure problem.
included.title: Cross platform, Multiple source, Monitoring and Trending Framework
